main: Hmmm? Why I haven't seen you before? Could you be the outsider from overseas?
What do you know about the Daimaou
branch_1: This place used to be called Gokuraku back in my day, but I think the kids call it something else now.
branch_3: Yes, the only way to get to Gokuraku is over the roiling seas and past the serpent of despair.
The only people who are here are those chosen by God. It's simple. If you're here, you must be one of the chosen.
Hmmm? Yomowho? Hirawhere? Are all outsiders as kooky as you?
